channel.title: Xiejra - Losing The Light [Dubstep]
channel.description:
Well i’m back again with yet another track. This is one of the tracks some more of you recognise already. This is probably some of my best work off the album so feedback would be really appreciated.
After this there will be only 2 more tracks to release... This time next week I will officially release my album. Stay tuned for my music in the future it will certainly be of a lot higher quality I promise.
Listen here | https://soundcloud.com/xiejramusic/losing-the-light
~X
